reviews.review_text: wow absolutely stunning show. emotive, sweet vocal improv, drums as potent and powerful as ever, bits rolling and haunting in places, filled with joy, jazz, pop, & pain. these were the shows for me. musicianship, emotion, and magic. thank you all.
